  </div>
 <div class="content-wrapper">
 <div class="the-640">
 <div class="wp-content">
 <p>It is such an honor for me to have the opportunity to study at BINUS University and obtain a master&#8217;s degree in business management. Aside from providing a good academic environment BINUS also gave me unforgettable experiences starting from learning in class to finally completing thesis and everything in the process. At BINUS I was taught to be able to develop my mindset value friendship also the importance of hard work perseverance and integrity. I learnt that score is just a number it doesn&#8217;t show how smart you are but it tells how responsible you are. So keep doing your best and enjoy all the process.</p>

